‼️one day Trip Near davangere‼️ unlimited food💯

📌 Utsav Rock Garden ☺️

Enjoy your vacation at the very acoustic, admirable, authentic Utsav Rock Garden we visited here and we learnt lot played and enjoyed a lot with my family and friends.

Here there are activities like boating, Kayaking, Rain Dance, Slides with Pool and lot more it is a perfect place to spend with your family and friends.

If we come to culture part there attires and clothing of particular regions from India as like Rajasthani, Uttar Karnataka, Lambani attires were available you can wear and get photoshoots.

If we come to food part the food was so good that lunch was fabulous there were lot of items that to with authentic Uttar Karnataka style. Don't miss thisss!!!.

Visit with Friends and family and enjoy your vacation.

Day out package: 850 rs per person include activities and unlimited food
